{"id":"summaries/2025-10-30-screenshot-2025-10-30-at-7-51-57-pm-b5317e6a","title":"Telnyx ticket #2 — opt-in screenshot needed for Outpace SMS","type":"summaries","html":"<p>Second <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/telnyx\">telnyx</a> toll-free verification rejection (Oct 29) — wants a <em>link to a screenshot of the opt-in form</em> with full CTIA disclosures. DBA explicitly listed as \"Outpace - iMessage Step Counter,\" confirming <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"projects/outpace\">outpace</a> is the SMS use-case underneath the <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/vrtl-pirates\">vrtl pirates</a> business name.</p>\n<p><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/telnyx\">telnyx</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/vrtl-pirates\">vrtl pirates</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"projects/outpace\">outpace</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/ctia-compliance\">ctia compliance</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/toll-free-verification\">toll free verification</a></p>\n","related":[{"id":"concepts/ctia-compliance","label":"CTIA Compliance"},{"id":"projects/outpace","label":"Outpace"},{"id":"entities/telnyx","label":"Telnyx"},{"id":"concepts/toll-free-verification","label":"Toll-Free Verification"},{"id":"entities/vrtl-pirates","label":"Vrtl Pirates"}]}
